<text top="80" left="85" width="522" height="16" font="0">Friday, 13 December 2013] 274 </text>
<text top="1197" left="83" width="447" height="11" font="2">INTERNAL QUESTION PAPER: NATIONAL COUNCIL OF PROVINCES NO 37─2013 </text>
<text top="120" left="299" width="300" height="19" font="10"><b>FRIDAY, 20 SEPTEMBER 2013 </b></text>
<text top="164" left="85" width="36" height="16" font="4"><b>362. </b></text>
<text top="164" left="139" width="569" height="16" font="4"><b>Mr S H Plaatjie (COPE-NW) to ask the Minister of Sport and Recreation:</b></text>
<text top="164" left="708" width="5" height="16" font="1"> </text>
<text top="205" left="139" width="674" height="16" font="1">Whether he has been informed that South African athletes do not receive any sponsors as a </text>
<text top="226" left="138" width="676" height="16" font="1">result of the various conflicts within Athletics South Africa; if not, what is the position in </text>
<text top="247" left="138" width="677" height="16" font="1">this regard; if so, (a) what steps has he taken to resolve this matter and (b) what are the </text>
<text top="267" left="138" width="175" height="16" font="1">further relevant details? </text>
<text top="269" left="752" width="56" height="13" font="13">CW493E</text>
<text top="267" left="808" width="5" height="16" font="1"> </text>
<text top="310" left="85" width="36" height="16" font="4"><b>363. </b></text>
<text top="310" left="139" width="569" height="16" font="4"><b>Mr S H Plaatjie (COPE-NW) to ask the Minister of Sport and Recreation:</b></text>
<text top="309" left="708" width="5" height="16" font="1"> </text>
<text top="351" left="139" width="28" height="16" font="1">(1) </text>
<text top="351" left="193" width="622" height="16" font="1">Whether he has been informed that the under-23 soccer team has not played any </text>
<text top="371" left="193" width="485" height="16" font="1">games in two years; if not, what is the position in this regard; if so, </text>
<text top="413" left="139" width="26" height="16" font="1">(2) </text>
<text top="413" left="193" width="620" height="16" font="1">whether the team will take part in the qualifying games for the next Olympics; if not, </text>
<text top="434" left="193" width="323" height="16" font="1">why not; if so, what are the relevant details? </text>
<text top="436" left="752" width="56" height="13" font="13">CW494E</text>
<text top="434" left="808" width="5" height="16" font="1"> </text>
<text top="477" left="311" width="276" height="19" font="10"><b>FRIDAY, 11 OCTOBER 2013 </b></text>
<text top="521" left="85" width="36" height="16" font="4"><b>365. </b></text>
<text top="521" left="139" width="614" height="16" font="4"><b>Mr D B Feldman (COPE-Gauteng) to ask the Minister of Sport and Recreation:</b></text>
<text top="521" left="753" width="5" height="16" font="1"> </text>
<text top="562" left="139" width="524" height="16" font="1">What are the reasons that led to the calling off of the Soweto Marathon? </text>
<text top="564" left="752" width="56" height="13" font="13">CW492E</text>
<text top="562" left="808" width="5" height="16" font="1"> </text>
<text top="605" left="311" width="276" height="19" font="10"><b>FRIDAY, 25 OCTOBER 2013 </b></text>
<text top="650" left="85" width="36" height="16" font="4"><b>425. </b></text>
<text top="650" left="139" width="463" height="16" font="4"><b>Mr D Joseph (DA-WC) to ask the President of the Republic:</b></text>
<text top="649" left="602" width="5" height="16" font="1"> </text>
<text top="691" left="139" width="675" height="16" font="1">(a) How many international trips has he undertaken during his first four years in office, (b) </text>
<text top="712" left="139" width="675" height="16" font="1">what was the total breakdown of the costs for each delegation regarding these trips and (c) </text>
<text top="732" left="139" width="511" height="16" font="1">what benefits has the country achieved as a direct result of these trips? </text>
<text top="734" left="752" width="56" height="13" font="13">CW635E</text>
<text top="732" left="808" width="5" height="16" font="1"> </text>
<text top="775" left="85" width="36" height="16" font="4"><b>426. </b></text>
<text top="775" left="139" width="548" height="16" font="4"><b>Mrs B L Abrahams (DA-Gauteng) to ask the President of the Republic:</b></text>
<text top="774" left="687" width="5" height="16" font="1"> </text>
<text top="816" left="139" width="27" height="16" font="1">(1) </text>
<text top="816" left="193" width="621" height="16" font="1">With reference to the President’s visit to Eldorado Park to address and discuss the </text>
<text top="836" left="193" width="621" height="16" font="1">escalating drug supply and abuse problem in the area, (a) how sustainable is the (i) </text>
<text top="857" left="193" width="622" height="16" font="1">Drug Master Plan and (ii) Gauteng Provincial Anti-Substance Abuse Strategy and </text>
<text top="878" left="193" width="491" height="16" font="1">(b) what is the current (i) status and (ii) progress of these strategies; </text>
<text top="919" left="139" width="26" height="16" font="1">(2) </text>
<text top="919" left="193" width="620" height="16" font="1">whether any other (a) programmes or (b) initiatives are being considered; if not, why </text>
<text top="940" left="193" width="622" height="16" font="1">not; if so, (i) when will these be undertaken or implemented and (ii) what are the </text>
<text top="961" left="193" width="172" height="16" font="1">further relevant details; </text>
<text top="1003" left="139" width="27" height="16" font="1">(3) </text>
<text top="1003" left="193" width="621" height="16" font="1">how many (a)(i) drug merchants and (ii) juveniles have been arrested and (b) were </text>
<text top="1023" left="193" width="242" height="16" font="1">released on bail since May 2013; </text>
<text top="1065" left="139" width="27" height="16" font="1">(4) </text>
<text top="1065" left="193" width="621" height="16" font="1">whether any rehabilitation centres will be built in Eldorado Park; if not, why not; if </text>
<text top="1086" left="193" width="77" height="16" font="1">so, when? </text>
<text top="1088" left="752" width="56" height="13" font="13">CW636E</text>
<text top="1086" left="808" width="5" height="16" font="1"> </text>
<text top="1129" left="139" width="5" height="19" font="10"><b> </b></text>
<text top="1129" left="355" width="5" height="19" font="10"><b> </b></text>
